highlights.text: Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “צמוד צמוד” is the highest at #3.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 323 weeks straight.
“אלוף העולם” by Hanan Ben Ari is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 70 spots at #105.
“The Code” by Nemo is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #16.
